cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with software engineering and specifically with the automatic inference of software architecture from source code. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category. The paper also involves clustering algorithms, which could fall under cs.PL (Programming Languages) or cs.SD (Software Development). The use of machine learning techniques for software analysis could also place the paper in cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper's focus on facilitating software maintenance could suggest a connection to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
